\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.1}{\ignorespaces Moment--0 maps of the Per-emb-2 streamer with overlaid best-fit models from the MCMC point method analysis. From left to right, the panels show the posterior peak solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_peak_grid}) and the posterior median solution (\ref {fig:per2_mcmc_mom0_median_grid}). In both cases, the solid curve traces the projected model streamer overlaid on the observed moment--0 emission, while the points indicate the centroid positions extracted from the data and used in the point method fitting. }}{25}{figure.caption.18}%
