\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {3.3}{\ignorespaces Position--velocity ($z$--$v$) diagrams of the Per-emb-2 streamer comparing the observed emission with the MCMC point method model predictions. The panels show the posterior peak (left panel) and posterior median (right panel) solutions. The background color map and contours represent the observed intensity distribution, while the solid curve traces the line-of-sight velocity along the model streamer. }}{27}{figure.caption.20}%
